    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use both for warehouses in which goods are stored until customs duties or taxes have been paid or for warehouses in which goods stored are insured against loss or damage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
